#: ../../T/tee.rst:7
msgid "n\\.,vt\\."
msgstr "名詞・他動詞"

#: ../../T/tee.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Purdue] A carbon copy of an electronic transmission. \"Oh, you're sending "
"him the :ref:`bits` to that? Slap on a tee for me.\" From the Unix command "
":manpage:`tee(1)`\\, itself named after a pipe fitting (see "
":ref:`plumbing`\\). Can also mean ‘save one for me’, as in \"Tee a slice for"
" me!\" Also spelled ‘T’."
msgstr ""
"[Purdue]電子的な送信の複写。「ああ、それの\\ :ref:`bits`\\ "
"を彼に送るのか?おれのためにteeを貼り付けてくれ」。Unixコマンドの\\ :manpage:`tee(1)`\\ "
"から。これ自体はパイプの継手にちなんで名付けられた(\\ :ref:`plumbing`\\ "
"参照)。「おれのために一つ取っておいて」という意味にもなり、\"Tee a slice for "
"me!\"(おれのために一切れ取っておいて!)のように使う。‘T’とも綴られる。"
